data.title: 2024 Puzzle 5: “Gold-Plated Record”
data.text:
Here’s contest puzzle #5. Solve using the Crossword Compiler applet below, download a PDF, or use Across Lite.

The meta is a hit single that has been certified gold (or higher) in eight countries.

Submit your answer to the meta using the form on the home page.

Gold-Plated Record by Will Pfadenhauer, Pete Muller, Mack Meller, and Andrew White
